></ul></dd></dl></header><main class="documentBody" data-lovdata-URL="LTII/forskrift/1996-08-28-876" id="dokument"><h1>Forskrift om bruk av beltemotorsykkel (snøscooter) på offentlige veger, Troms.</h1><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTII/forskrift/1996-08-28-876/§1" data-name="§1" data-partID="§1" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/" id="paragraf-1"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 1</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1">Bruk av beltemotorsykkel (snøscooter) er forbudt på samtlige riks- og fylkesveger i Troms fylke.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/2/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-2">Bruk av beltemotorsykkel (snøscooter) er forbudt på følgende kommunale veger i Troms fylke;<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Balsfjord kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/3/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-3">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Bardu kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/4/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-4">Samtlige veger i boligfeltene samt<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/4/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-4-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/4/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-4-punkt-1-ledd-1">Fosshaug bru – Strømsmo</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/4/punkt/2/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-4-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/4/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-4-punkt-2-ledd-1">Fosshaug bru – Østhagen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/4/punkt/3/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-4-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/4/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-4-punkt-3-ledd-1">Fosshaug bru – x Rv 847 (Vikingkrysset).</article></article></li></ul><p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Dyrøy Kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Gratangen kommune:</i></p><ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-1-ledd-1">Kryss E6 – Øse (veis ende)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/2/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-2-ledd-1">Kryss E6 – Kvernmo (veis ende)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/3/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-3-ledd-1">Strekningen Storfossen – Gratangen turiststasjon – kryss E6 – kryss Rv. 825 – Labergdalen (veis ende)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/4/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-4-ledd-1">Kommunal veg fra Foldvik bru – Hellarbogen, kryss Rv 825</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/5/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/5/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-5-punkt-5-ledd-1">Samtlige veger i boligfeltene.</article></article></li></ul><p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Harstad kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/6/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-6">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Ibestad kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/7/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-7">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Karlsøy kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/8/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-8">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Kvæfjord kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/9/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-9">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Kvænangen kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10">Samtlige kommunale veger, med unntak av:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-1-ledd-1">Fv. 367 – Vangen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/2/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-2-ledd-1">Valahamn – Indre Valan</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/3/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-3-ledd-1">Veg i Indre Olderfjord</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/4/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-4-ledd-1">Veg på Spildra</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/5/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-5-ledd-1">Nordstrøm – Kollerbukt</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/6/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-6"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/6/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-6-ledd-1">Veg i Reinfjord</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/7/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-7"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/7/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-7-ledd-1">Fv. 367 – Løkviknesset</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/8/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-8"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/10/punkt/8/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-10-punkt-8-ledd-1">Kommunal veg Segelvik – Finnmark grense</article></article></li></ul><p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Kåfjord kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/11/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-11">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Lavangen kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/12/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-12">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Lenvik kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/13/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-13">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Lyngen kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/14/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-14">Samtlige kommunale veger, med unntak av:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/14/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-14-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/14/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-14-punkt-1-ledd-1">Storåsvegen i Nord-Lenangen.</article></article></li></ul><p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Målselv kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/15/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-15">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Nordreisa kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/16/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-16">Samtlige kommunale veger, med unntak av:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/16/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-16-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/16/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-16-punkt-1-ledd-1">Svartfossvegen.</article></article></li></ul><p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Salangen kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/17/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-17">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Skjervøy kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/18/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-18">Kommunale veger på Skjervøy tettsted.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Skånland kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/19/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-19">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Storfjord kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/20/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-20">Samtlige kommunale veger, med unntak av:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/20/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-20-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/20/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-20-punkt-1-ledd-1">Eggaveien</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/20/punkt/2/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-20-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/20/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-20-punkt-2-ledd-1">Signalnes – Poras</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/20/punkt/3/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-20-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/20/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="par