edd-21-punkt-1-ledd-1">Rabbås – Lynghaug</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/21/punkt/2/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-21-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/21/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-21-punkt-2-ledd-1">Skarvegen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/21/punkt/3/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-21-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/21/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-21-punkt-3-ledd-1">Sørhusvegen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/21/punkt/4/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-21-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/21/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-21-punkt-4-ledd-1">x Rv. 84 – Vestgård – Nygård (Gumpedalen)</article></article></li></ul><p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Torsken kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/22/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-22">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Tranøy kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/23/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-23">Samtlige kommunale veger.<p class="leddfortsettelse"><i>Tromsø kommune:</i></p></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/24/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-24">Samtlige kommunale veger.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTII/forskrift/1996-08-28-876/§2" data-name="§2" data-partID="§2" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/" id="paragraf-2"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 2</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1">Forskriften trer i kraft 1. januar 1997. Fra samme tidspunkt oppheves forskrifter gitt den 16. januar 1992 nr. 110 om bruk av beltemotorsykkel (snøscooter) på offentlige veger, Troms.</article></article></main></body></html>